{"tid":1532592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612眼中槍老師表揚罷課學生！","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:20:11.000Z","uid":288970,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dedfd84ed89bec9de6c69bf3d71ac460ee674801","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"中學生今日好波，連老師都讚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n今天或者是<span style=\"color: red;\">香港有史以來最大規模的中學生罷課運動</span>。學生也站出來了，老師實在沒有理由不發聲，獨善其身。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當政權還在煞有介事地警告學生不要欺凌警察子女，學生們卻胸懷磊落</span>，付出更大的代價證明自己的理直氣壯。<br />\n<br />\n後果：學習受阻、家庭爭執、校方處分。在今天的香港，還要面對隨時被武裝警員查問搜身，甚至是被惡勢力襲擊的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n對於罷課或校內抗爭，學生們比誰都更清楚，承擔的比誰都要多，而他們仍然在本是理所當然的安逸中選擇挑戰社會的恐怖，並戰勝了自己內心的恐懼。<span style=\"color: red;\">不論政見，這一份勇氣都值得所有同年人與成年人尊敬。</span><br />\n<br />\n我個人和所認識的老師都不希望學生罷課。但學生同為社會一員，與所有市民一樣經歷了香港六月以來的執法和制度暴力。<span style=\"color: red;\">若單以訓導方式阻嚇學生運動，壓抑他們與生俱來的惻隱之心與正義感，我們又是在培養怎麼樣的下一代？</span><br />\n<br />\n學生的義憤，不應被打壓，而是要被教育工作者和成年人正面面對。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100004203397436/posts/1423804247769675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100004203397436%2Fposts%2F1423804247769675&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1au6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=f69d6908\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100004203397436/posts/1423804247769675</a><br />\n<br />\n正評為中學生打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f089669cd3eee1853f6822a8636360ce5fe13b15","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"705a9c0da3e074e4be0a3eba37121d09f3d3251c","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"4d11477300610eb91751d58fd85ee888ad28efbe","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"到"},{"pid":"f24cd11c9f957cc9a1890c9f61d0a00091a66f9b","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"2ee8f02ae115ab22222d5e2146f755fea7a78da2","tid":1532592,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"反送中就係香港「五四運動」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>外爭港權，內除港賊</strong></span></span><br />\n（對抗中共侵權，懲處媚共官員）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「德先生」，你好嗎？</span></span><br />\n（和民主Democracy say hi)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寧為玉碎，不為瓦全</span></strong>（真係五四運動口號）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">（一百年前都識我要攬炒！）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#Chinazi"},{"pid":"fbabc8bf95c96598921b50eaae5a3c1cc5e1807e","tid":1532592,"uid":288970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"請幫忙"},{"pid":"f63b444cc2f070b26e0898c82e59f77d9347772d","tid":1532592,"uid":47876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"push"}]}